1. U pustinji *nema* puno ljudi. (In the desert, *there are* not many people.)
2. Videli smo *ogromne* peščane dine u pustinji. (We saw *huge* sand dunes in the desert.)
3. Pustinjski vetrovi *pušu* u ovo doba godine. (Desert winds *blow* at this time of the year.)
4. Vojska se *sakrila* u pustinji tokom rata. (The army *hid* in the desert during the war.)
5. Pustinjska klima je *neprijateljska* za životinje i biljke. (Desert climate is *hostile* to animals and plants.)
6. Putovao sam kroz pustinju pešice *nedeljama*. (I traveled through the desert *on foot* for weeks.)
7. *Usamljenost* u pustinji može biti veoma teška. (The *loneliness* in the desert can be very difficult.)
8. *Preživeti* u pustinji zahteva posebne veštine i opremu. (To *survive* in the desert, special skills and equipment are required.)
9. Pustinjski pejzaž *inspiriše* umetnike širom sveta. (The desert landscape *inspires* artists around the world.)
10. *Oasis* u sredini pustinje je blagoslov za umorne putnike. (An *oasis* in the middle of the desert is a blessing for weary travelers.)